Jessalyn Gilsig https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jessalyn_Gilsig 0 Jessalyn Sarah Gilsig (born November 30, 1971) is a Canadian-American actress known for her roles in television series, e.g. as Lauren Davis in Boston Public, Gina Russo in Nip/Tuck, Terri Schuester in Glee, and as Siggy Haraldson on the History Channel series Vikings.
